  <brief_title>Positron Emission Tomography (PET)-Computed Tomography (CT) in Inflammatory Bowel Disease (IBD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study of the Role of PET-CT for Diagnosis and Assessment of Therapeutic Efficacy in Inflammatory Bowel Disease</official_title>
